#	Communications Protocol Test Script
#	Order Test
#	Send three packets
#	Trash the middle one
#	This script seems to work

#	start up the client
PInit
TInit
POpen 1
TOpen

#	write 40 bytes of random data 3 times
#	trash the second packet
WAIT 1
BEEP
TWriteDataASync 40

BEEP
TRASHCRC
TWriteDataASync 41

BEEP
TWriteDataASync 42

WAIT 600

#	close down the connection
TClose
PClose
BEEP
